    <arm_group_label>CHOD + BVAM + WBRT</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Patients 70 years old and younger with newly diagnosed, biopsy-proven PCNSL received one cycle of CHOD followed by two cycles of BVAM. Patients then received WBRT, 30.6 Gy, if a complete response was evoked, or 50.4 Gy if the response was less than complete; both doses were given in 1.8-Gy daily fractions.</description>
